Summary
========
1) Identified Vulnerabilities: SQL injection on login forms and XSS in feedback forms.

2) Fixes Applied: Implemented parameterized queries, user input validation, and HTML encoding.

3) Copilot’s Assistance: Provided secure coding examples, debugging techniques, and test cases to verify fixes.

Folder Structure
================

SecureWebApp/
├── Models/
│   └── UserModel.cs
├── Controllers/
│   └── AccountController.cs
├── Views/
│   ├── Shared/
│   │   └── _Layout.cshtml
│   └── Account/
│       └── Login.cshtml
├── Services/
│   └── SecurityService.cs
├── Tests/
│   └── SecurityTests.cs
